OL,3,CBritish dad 'killed in Ukraine by
OL,4,CRussian drone'
OL,6,FA British dad who volunteered to fight
OL,7,Ffor Ukraine despite having no military
OL,8,Fexperience has been killed by a
OL,9,FRussian drone in his first mission,
OL,10,Fhis wife has said.
OL,12,FAlan Robert Williams, 35, who has a 12-
OL,13,Fyear-old daughter, has officially been
OL,14,Fdeclared as Missing In Action because
OL,15,Fhis body has yet to be retrieved.
