OL,3,CBritish dad 'killed in Ukraine by
OL,4,CRussian drone'
OL,6,FHis wife, Stephanie, 40, who pleaded
OL,7,Fwith Alan not to go, was told by her
OL,8,Fhusband's unit that he had been killed
OL,9,Fin the Kharkiv region on 14 July while
OL,10,Ftrying to retrieve some foreign
OL,11,Fofficers.
OL,13,FStephanie was told that four Russian
OL,14,Fdrones dropped a mortar eight metres
OL,15,Ffrom the team, killing Alan instantly.
OL,17,F"He only signed his contract with the
OL,18,Funit on the 10 June", Stephanie said.
OL,19,F"He had only been there a month. He
OL,20,Fhad no frontline military experience
OL,21,Fat all.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
