OL,3,CBritish dad 'killed in Ukraine by
OL,4,CRussian drone'
OL,6,F"Even though I can't dispute the
OL,7,Faccounts I've been given from numerous
OL,8,Fpeople I have spoken to out there, it
OL,9,Fstill doesn't feel real.
OL,11,F"I've been sending him messages on his
OL,12,Fphone giving him updates as to what
OL,13,Fhas been going on."
OL,15,FAfter being discharged from hospital
OL,16,Ffor struggling with his mental health,
OL,17,Fthe dad, from Wirral, volunteered to
OL,18,Ffight for Ukraine, despite his loved
OL,19,Fones pleading with him not to.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
