OL,3,CBritish dad 'killed in Ukraine by
OL,4,CRussian drone'
OL,6,FStephanie believes he initially
OL,7,Fapplied "because of his mental health"
OL,8,Fbut, since he has been away, he told
OL,9,Fhis friends he "couldn't sit by and
OL,10,Fwatch what was happening to the
OL,11,Fcivilians, especially the children".
OL,13,FShe said: "When it came to children he
OL,14,Fhad a massive heart. It gave him
OL,15,Fpurpose. That is what a few of the
OL,16,Flads out there said, he finally felt
OL,17,Fthat he wasn't failing people."
OL,26,@uD@KOU
