OL,3,CBritish dad 'killed in Ukraine by
OL,4,CRussian drone'
OL,6,FAlan went to Ukraine on 7 May where he
OL,7,Funderwent training and he seemed in
OL,8,Fmuch better form in the first few
OL,9,Fconversations with Stephanie, who
OL,10,F"feared the worst" from day one.
OL,12,FHowever, while his mental health
OL,13,Fimproved, Stephanie's declined, and
OL,14,Fshe said it was like they had switched.
OL,16,FThe last time Stephanie spoke to Alan
OL,17,Fwas on 2 July when his tone suddenly
OL,18,Fchanged, after he told her he was
OL,19,Fembarking on his first mission.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@RO]
