OL,3,CBritish dad 'killed in Ukraine by
OL,4,CRussian drone'
OL,6,F"I could tell by the way he was
OL,7,Ftalking to me it was a dangerous
OL,8,Fmission," she said.
OL,10,FStephanie was contacted by Ukrainian
OL,11,Fsergeant a few weeks later, who told
OL,12,Fher that "all the evidence showed he
OL,13,Fwas killed in action."
OL,15,FThen, on 30 July, a man who was with
OL,16,FAlan from the moment he arrived in
OL,17,FUkraine to the mission itself, called
OL,18,Fher.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@IO]
