OL,3,CBritish dad 'killed in Ukraine by
OL,4,CRussian drone'
OL,6,FHe said in no uncertain terms that he
OL,7,Fhad passed away on the battlefield and
OL,8,Fthey did everything they could to
OL,9,Fbring him back, but being under
OL,10,Fambush, it was too dangerous.
OL,12,FStephanie said it will not sink in
OL,13,Funtil he is officially declared Killed
OL,14,FIn Action. But for this to happen, his
OL,15,Fbody needs to be retrieved, or in six
OL,16,Fmonths time she can apply to the
OL,17,FUkrainian courts to have him declared
OL,18,Fdead.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
