OL,3,CBritish dad 'killed in Ukraine by
OL,4,CRussian drone'
OL,6,FStephanie, a civil servant and call
OL,7,Fhandler, said: "We have lost Alan's
OL,8,Fwage completely which was half of our
OL,9,Fbills. I can't claim anything with
OL,10,Fregards to being a widow until he is
OL,11,Fofficially declared.
OL,13,F"I am not entitled to anything. I earn
OL,14,Ftoo much to claim any single person
OL,15,Fbenefit and I have two adult children
OL,16,Fwho count towards people in my house
OL,17,Fso I can't claim anything at all.
OL,26,@oD@POUuD@AOU
