OL,6,F"At the moment I have a tiny buffer
OL,7,Fbut once that finishes I will not be
OL,8,Fable to afford bills or rent or
OL,9,Fanything like that."
OL,11,FStephanie's mum, Lynne, from Upton,
OL,12,Fhas since launched a GoFundMe to help
OL,13,Fher daughter pay for rent and bills
OL,14,F"during this difficult time."
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the Foreign,
OL,17,FCommonwealth & Development Office told
OL,18,Fus: "We are supporting the family of a
OL,19,FBritish man who is missing in Ukraine
OL,20,Fand are in contact with the local
OL,21,Fauthorities."
